        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued July 1 at 6:19PM MDT until July 1 at 6:45PM MDT by NWS Great Falls MT</headline>
        <description>At 618 PM MDT, a severe thunderstorm was located near Townsend,
moving east at 30 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Expect damage to roofs, siding, and trees.

This severe thunderstorm will remain over mainly rural areas of east
central Broadwater County.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
